{"tid":538982,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"Third hon認真一問","createTime":"2018-01-24T06:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T10:00:57.000Z","uid":114392,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"0085eb162a29e39e9627fb67b96f84d4cfa7863a","tid":538982,"uid":114392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T06:58:27.000Z","msg":"三大science<br />\n3rd hon畢業<br />\n會唔會之後無人請<br />\n政府個啲會唔會完全唔請3rd hon<br />\nfg出黎係咪極睇重hon<br />\n小弟諗緊去唔去進修/讀其他課程<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知道自己好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係垃圾我係廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身自己大學揀錯科 自dse完左開始無認真讀過書<br />\n大學讀得辛苦又唔敢quit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出到黎唔打算做返science相關既工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲打可以比啲意見/經驗小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求認真回覆 好迷惘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf78691f43e34c3453803e46ebe68e164b0d8c55","tid":538982,"uid":157994,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:02:41.000Z","msg":"No one cares after first year"},{"pid":"e500d06bff13fd4f44d9b322b5f875ac6534dcdc","tid":538982,"uid":114392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:15:15.000Z","msg":"pushhhh"},{"pid":"34eb9cc4296d3d050cd9f920c562c9a31ab71c3a","tid":538982,"uid":134969,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:26:07.000Z","msg":"政府公務員同細公司就唔太睇咩hon<br />\n<br />\n但讀science 就好似無咩公司會請science ，唯有考慮下考公務員"},{"pid":"7f1058ce3705675eba74d2e43db84cc2492b293b","tid":538982,"uid":8318,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:27:17.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"b4b0a98e3972fc6232406907f3407c0e71fb2c67","tid":538982,"uid":152244,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:28:14.000Z","msg":"讀個專科hd,穩下食無難度"},{"pid":"1f68be80be5fe325141b1ebc4fff3b0ee5c24d1c","tid":538982,"uid":114392,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府公務員同細公司就唔太睇咩hon<br />\n<br />\n但讀science 就好似無咩公司會請science ，唯有考慮下考公務員</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n申請做啲高級啲既 例如eo 係咪會唔請嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a75e63bb9f341c010c8fb2b43546adeec238a37","tid":538982,"uid":114392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:31:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀個專科hd,穩下食無難度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無咩好介紹 同埋要讀幾耐到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0fdfa50d0dba3a9ba043ee62fa34005bf1e43a","tid":538982,"uid":76931,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:33:09.000Z","msg":"留名等睇拎third hon 月入50k嘅人"},{"pid":"c166203c089461b2d7fd8be8ab6878bdd0c97b21","tid":538982,"uid":165377,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名等睇拎third hon 月入50k嘅人</blockquote><br />\n連登中五仔都100k la<br />\n利申月入18萬<br />\n工種免問 問即係你唔信"},{"pid":"ce08173acedabc8d0b895b701841dc328223eeb1","tid":538982,"uid":22302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:42:27.000Z","msg":"無認真讀但讀得辛苦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14754c7eacc75d7ca25b6dfb6e92db3a23fa6b46","tid":538982,"uid":122743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:44:02.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"690288f0015989cb8976832e6895cf66c8ded57b","tid":538982,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b0fdfa50d0dba3a9ba043ee62fa34005bf1e43a","tid":538982,"uid":76931,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:33:09.000Z","msg":"留名等睇拎third hon 月入50k嘅人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596ac9fa8e6e00b8590ba5d5a269bae0cfa79d0e","tid":538982,"uid":114392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:03:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無認真讀但讀得辛苦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該話認真咗一陣覺得辛苦 所以又hea住讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48cfd2906588d04c074df38d33d24185ba5dee1","tid":538982,"uid":114392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名等睇拎third hon 月入50k嘅人</blockquote><br />\n連登中五仔都100k la<br />\n利申月入18萬<br />\n工種免問 問即係你唔信</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真post求認真回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b065da14b93108f063daa25cf50c4690aa6606c","tid":538982,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:06:37.000Z","msg":"本身science好難搵工"},{"pid":"9131e7eafee0927f8399835fcdc8c983e4ac84be","tid":538982,"uid":76681,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:14:23.000Z","msg":"大把成功例子：<br />\n<br />\n港大校長<span style=\"color: red;\">徐立之</span>在中大攻讀生物系學士時，只取得三級榮譽畢業<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但3 hon點都有影響:<br />\n1. 唔洗唸大公司mt /  大學入面pc/ EO 以上機會好細<br />\n2. AO EO等機會好細<br />\n3. 見工會比人壓價  / 面試機會少過1ST, 2ND UP<br />\n4. 讀勁野MASTER 好難<br />\n5. 唔敢講比人聽 3大但 3 HON<br />\n6. 樣衰, 人生污點"},{"pid":"9483675861b03424233d1ee93135fe336e9767d7","tid":538982,"uid":58402,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:20:32.000Z","msg":"本人 物理third hon 係日校教緊物理數學<br />\n<br />\n雖然好慚愧，但只要個人presentable 都有出路既"},{"pid":"8fb2f233d143a1b924319b25a5089a69834c17ba","tid":538982,"uid":114392,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:42:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大把成功例子：<br />\n<br />\n港大校長<span style=\"color: red;\">徐立之</span>在中大攻讀生物系學士時，只取得三級榮譽畢業<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但3 hon點都有影響:<br />\n1. 唔洗唸大公司mt /  大學入面pc/ EO 以上機會好細<br />\n2. AO EO等機會好細<br />\n3. 見工會比人壓價  / 面試機會少過1ST, 2ND UP<br />\n4. 讀勁野MASTER 好難<br />\n5. 唔敢講比人聽 3大但 3 HON<br />\n6. 樣衰, 人生污點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2個到聽聞真係百幾人爭一個ao/eo位，所以應該爭唔贏<br />\n<br />\n3個到都預左，宜家唯有努力啲去學好啲英文，講流利啲，同埋睇下有無咩其他技能equip下自己<br />\n<br />\n4應該唔諗住讀，除非讀完有好既出路，因為諗住搵多啲錢，同埋讀完個degree拎個3rd hon，唔敢同屋企人再拎錢書<br />\n<br />\n5同6就真係....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比我再揀一次一定努力啲讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e2568cad6d562e150a15df6517aabcc98e0b4b","tid":538982,"uid":114392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本人 物理third hon 係日校教緊物理數學<br />\n<br />\n雖然好慚愧，但只要個人presentable 都有出路既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n起碼物理都叫難啲既科，我讀緊啲易少少既major<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好慚愧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319072e7502f548d0adab08e3b65cdb303777624","tid":538982,"uid":114392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身science好難搵工</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係...<br />\n我又唔係讀得勁，應該搵份唔關science事既工做會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4314ca11b58b33f899f2ae81ff6f77253998ca50","tid":538982,"uid":90023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:46:05.000Z","msg":"我都sci 3rd hon啦 又咪係咁"},{"pid":"c164f6e678170342d0a3aa7e9b9641c2e13c59e6","tid":538982,"uid":30762,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:46:43.000Z","msg":"科大就科大<br />\n咩撚野三大<br />\n利申：UST"},{"pid":"2b00fac01e004f38b222c66589413123e4a3a77c","tid":538982,"uid":114392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:55:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都sci 3rd hon啦 又咪係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁請問巴打出路好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 純粹好奇"},{"pid":"4ae0feb6e25e21623d15f1e1f08b99cdcf7070c6","tid":538982,"uid":114392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:56:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>科大就科大<br />\n咩撚野三大<br />\n利申：UST</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊間大學唔係最重要<br />\n3rd hon先係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aafeaa1d1b51edf0d126098f8827e7c3233dac7","tid":538982,"uid":38461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf78691f43e34c3453803e46ebe68e164b0d8c55","tid":538982,"uid":157994,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T07:02:41.000Z","msg":"No one cares after first year"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:57:25.000Z","msg":"我返左工3年左右去in港燈 佢有問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大公司應該會問"},{"pid":"a3941cc399075cf2ad5e9ed88c98970142f5dbfc","tid":538982,"uid":90023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b00fac01e004f38b222c66589413123e4a3a77c","tid":538982,"uid":114392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:55:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都sci 3rd hon啦 又咪係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁請問巴打出路好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 純粹好奇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:58:24.000Z","msg":"暫時還可以做sales狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bde5da1e37869e6ee9a9cd4ef3fa97cb4e8d186","tid":538982,"uid":114392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T09:00:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都sci 3rd hon啦 又咪係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n